lead_paragraph: Renault driver Kevin Magnussen will have to pass a fitness check at Monza on Thursday before being cleared to race in the Italian Grand Prix after his big crash in Belgium last weekend.

headline.print_headline: Confident Magnussen Needs Fitness Check at Monza
